                    text: "The LF1 offers exceptional performance and smooth operation, but early models (2016–2017) had reliability concerns, particularly high-pressure fuel pump wear. Later revisions (post-2018) improved component durability, so well-maintained examples can exceed 120,000 km. Regular servicing with GM-specified oil (5W-30 dexos1 Gen 3) and timely fuel system maintenance greatly enhance longevity.",
