                    text: "Yes, extensively. ECU remaps can safely yield +50–90 kW on stage 1, as the engine responds well to tuning. Supporting modifications like intercooler, exhaust, and pulley upgrades can further improve performance. The forged internals handle high boost increases, making it a favorite among enthusiasts. However, upgraded fuel systems are recommended for higher power levels.",
